description: [``botocore``] This release provides a way to search for existing tags within an instance. Before tagging a resource, ensure consistency by searching for pre-existing key:value pairs.
[``botocore``] Timestamp Starting Position For Kinesis and Kafka Data Sources in a Glue Streaming Job
[``botocore``] Add support for user.extra.sessionName in Kubernetes Audit Logs Findings.
[``botocore``] Support for a new API "GetMFADevice" to present MFA device metadata such as device certifications
[``botocore``] Added time zone estimation support for journeys
